sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant MLPod as ML Workload Pod
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over MLPod,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking

    MLPod->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>HTTPS 8443 | Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>Proxy: Validate SA Token<br/>against K8s API
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>HTTP 5000 (pod-local)
    MLflow->>MLflow: Resolve workspace from<br/>X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE header
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>PostgreSQL TLS 1.2+ | User/Pass
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact (model file)<br/>HTTPS 443 | AWS IAM / Access Key
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow-->>Proxy: JSON Response
    Proxy-->>MLPod: HTTPS Response

    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FedUI as MLflow Federated UI<br/>5000/TCP via Gateway

    Note over Browser,FedUI: Flow 2: UI Embedding via Module Federation

    Browser->>Dashboard: Navigate to experiments<br/>HTTPS 443 | OAuth/OIDC
    Dashboard->>FedUI: Load remoteEntry.js<br/>HTTPS via Gateway | Bearer Token
    FedUI-->>Dashboard: Federated components loaded
    FedUI->>MLflow: GET /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>HTTPS via Gateway | Bearer Token
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments<br/>PostgreSQL TLS 1.2+
    PG-->>MLflow: Experiment data
    MLflow-->>FedUI: JSON Response

    participant OTelSDK as OpenTelemetry SDK
    Note over OTelSDK,PG: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    OTelSDK->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>HTTP 5000 | Protobuf binary | Bearer Token
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>PostgreSQL TLS 1.2+
    PG-->>MLflow: Stored
    MLflow-->>OTelSDK: 200 OK

    participant Client as Client Application
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic/etc.)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 4: AI Gateway LLM Proxy

    Client->>MLflow: POST /gateway/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 5000 | Bearer Token
    MLflow->>MLflow: Decrypt provider API key<br/>(KEK envelope encryption)
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS 443 | Provider API Key
    LLM-->>MLflow: Completion response
    MLflow-->>Client: Proxied JSON response
